title: More simple accessibility to night mode UI on Sushi Swap
body: The new UI is great however it is hard to find night mode version of the website for us night owls. My Firefox browser is setup with an extension to automatically turn websites into night mode however when I try to use the website on the go or through Status Wallet the blinding page pops up and the night mode is in-existent or hard to find. I would like to propose an easy to access night mode. Thank you community!
choices: Easy to access night mode button
